### 06 — Criar Playlist
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contas/{{contaId}}/playlists
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Minha Playlist Top"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("playlistId", response.body.id);
  client.log("Playlist criada: " + response.body.id);
%}

###

### 06b — Listar Playlists da Conta
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contas/{{contaId}}/playlists

###

### 06c — Adicionar Música na Playlist
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/playlists/{{playlistId}}/musicas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contaId": "{{contaId}}",
  "musicaId": "{{musicaId}}"
}

###

### 06d — Erro: adicionar a mesma música duas vezes (deve retornar 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/playlists/{{playlistId}}/musicas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contaId": "{{contaId}}",
  "musicaId": "{{musicaId}}"
}

###

### 06e — Remover Música da Playlist
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/contas/{{contaId}}/playlists/{{playlistId}}/musicas/{{musicaId}}
